Class RegressionTreeModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.streaminer.stream.classifier.tree.RegressionTreeModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Model, PredictionModel<Data,Double>

    public class RegressionTreeModel
extends Object
implements PredictionModel<Data,Double>

    This class implements a regression tree model. A regression tree model is a decision tree with regression models at its leaf nodes.

    Author:
    Christian Bockermann <christian.bockermann@udo.edu>
